rd(은)는 21세였고, 그의 어머니 Lady Alice Tendering(은)는 22세였다. 그는 Mary Hussey(와)과 적어도 한 명의 딸을 두었다. 그는 1436년 2월 14일 영국 에세스 베더스필드에서 48세의 나이로 사망했으며 영국 수폴크 스토크 비 나이랜드에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"12 March 1387–14 February 1436":"1387. gada 12. marts–1436. gada 14. februāris","1385–1436":"1385–1436","1387–1436":"1387–1436","1398–1447":"1398–1447","1428–1483":"1428–1483","1366–1437":"1366–1437","1365–1426":"1365–1426","18 October 1426":"1426. gada 18. oktobris","before 1385":"pirms 1385. gada","1385":"1385","1483":"1483","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1447":"1447","1436":"1436","14 February 1436":"1436. gada 14. februāris","1366":"1366","1365":"1365","1398":"1398","1387":"1387","26 August 1428":"1428. gada 26. augusts","1428":"1428","12 March 1387":"1387. gada 12. marts","Wethersfield, Essex, England":"Wethersfield, Essex, England","Stoke by Nayland, Suffolk, England":"Stoke by Nayland, Suffolk, England","England":"England","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, England"},"mg":{"12 March 1387–14 February 1436":"12 martsa 1387–14 febroary 1436","1385–1436":"1385–1436","1387–1436":"1387–1436","1398–1447":"1398–1447","1428–1483":"1428–1483","1366–1437":"1366–1437","1365–1426":"1365–1426","18 October 1426":"18 ôktôbra 1426","before 1385":"talohan'ny 1385","1385":"1385","1483":"1483","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1447":"1447","1436":"1436","14 February 1436":"14 febroary 1436","1366":"1366","1365":"1365","1398":"1398","1387":"1387","26 August 1428":"26 aogôsitra 1428","1428":"1428","12 March 1387":"12 martsa 1387","Wethersfield, Essex, England":"Wethersfield, Essex, England","Stoke by Nayland, Suffolk, England":"Stoke by Nayland, Suffolk, England","England":"England","Suffolk, England":"Suffolk, England"},"ms":{"12 March 1387–14 February 1436":"12 Mac 1387–14 Februari 1436","1385–1436":"1385–1436","1387–1436":"1387–1436","1398–1447":"1398–1447","1428–1483":"1428–1483","1366–1437":"1366–1437","1365–1426":"1365–1426","18 October 1426":"18 Oktober 1426","before 1385":"sebelum 1385","1385":"1385","1483":"1483","1426"